70
00:03:47.685 --> 00:03:50.980
We've already planned
our honeymoon in Thailand.

71
00:03:51.564 --> 00:03:55.068
Professionally speaking.
I'm at the top of my game.

72
00:03:56.069 --> 00:03:58.613
But that asshole is somehow always there.

73
00:03:58.696 --> 00:04:01.032
I feel like he's stalking me. like he's…

74
00:04:01.115 --> 00:04:03.326
constantly keeping an eye on me.

75
00:04:04.285 --> 00:04:06.371
[man] That's the nature of trauma. Camila.

76
00:04:06.454 --> 00:04:08.289
It's gonna take more
than a couple sessions

77
00:04:08.373 --> 00:04:11.376
to heal from the negative experiences
you suffered a year and a half ago.

78
00:04:13.503 --> 00:04:15.213
This dream you're describing.

79
00:04:16.130 --> 00:04:17.548
the recurring one.

80
00:04:17.632 --> 00:04:18.716
