for my social media campaign.

96
00:05:14.689 --> 00:05:17.150
and that's it. I'll be ready to leave.

97
00:05:17.233 --> 00:05:19.861
[David] Do beautiful girl bosses
like you ever get to rest?

98
00:05:19.944 --> 00:05:22.363
Well. this girl boss
has to lead by example.

99
00:05:22.447 --> 00:05:23.281
[chuckles]

100
00:05:23.364 --> 00:05:25.533
All right. my love. See you soon. right?

101
00:05:25.616 --> 00:05:26.701
I'm sorry. I won't.

102
00:05:26.784 --> 00:05:28.786
The girls and I also made plans tonight.

103
00:05:29.287 --> 00:05:31.831
You think you're the only one
who's gonna have a bachelor party?

104
00:05:31.914 --> 00:05:34.625
My love. tomorrow I need you
to be rested and look perfect

105
00:05:34.709 --> 00:05:38.087
and be ready to meet me at the altar
to say. "Yes. I do."

106
00:05:38.171 --> 00:05:39.005
Listen. baby.

107
00:05:39.714 --> 00:05:43.134
I love you with all of my heart.
Camila Román.

108
00:05:43.217 --> 00:05:45.720
I love you so much.
I can't wait to kiss you. babe.

109
00:05:47.972 --> 00:05:49.891
[crowd cheering]

110
00:05:49.974 --> 00:05:52.518
["Kintsugi" continues]

111
00:05:54.479 --> 00:05:55.521
[dramatic sting]

112
00:05:59.484 --> 00:06:00.401
