113
00:06:00.485 --> 00:06:04.280
[reporter] After the scandal that shocked
the Colombian society in 2023.

114
00:06:04.364 --> 00:06:07.116
Ángela Ferrer was sentenced
to five years in federal prison

115
00:06:07.200 --> 00:06:11.037
for the first-degree murder of her father.
businessman Pedro Ferrer.

116
00:06:11.120 --> 00:06:15.124
However. Ángela Ferrer only served
an 18-month sentence.

117
00:06:15.208 --> 00:06:18.753
Tomorrow. the architect and businesswoman
will be released.

118
00:06:19.379 --> 00:06:21.672
-["Kintsugi" continues]
-[cheering continues]

119
00:06:28.888 --> 00:06:31.265
[cheering continues]

120
00:06:52.328 --> 00:06:53.246
[cheering]

121
00:06:53.329 --> 00:06:55.415
["Kintsugi" continues]

122
00:07:31.284 --> 00:07:32.368
