["Buri Buri" by Daniela Sarria playing]

125
00:07:47.675 --> 00:07:49.677
[laughing]

126
00:07:49.760 --> 00:07:51.012
Whoo!

127
00:07:51.095 --> 00:07:54.015
-I'm making a video!
-Please promise we won't lose you.

128
00:07:54.098 --> 00:07:56.684
You will never. ever lose me. You won't.

129
00:07:56.767 --> 00:07:58.311
